title: Linuxfest was dope and you're lame if you didn't come.
description:
We skipped all the talks, went to fancy restaurants, play libre GNU/Linux video games and went to an Orthodox Church. You don't even need to watch the video because the title says it all.

I will be back at Linuxfest Southeast in 2023.
